message.raw:
Close branch. Default branch is now where the gtk version lives, until
the Qt port is stable, when it will be merged in, replacing the gtk version there.

The sole change I made in this branch didn't work anyway, as we were actually
using features from gtk 2.24, and I would had to have made additional changes
in order to be compatible with 2.22.
